<p align="left">This site provides safety training information on the  current training schedule and materials available for use by the  university departments and colleges.</p>
<h3><a href="Documents/Admin_Offices/Facilities Management/Security and Safety/Firesafetypresentation1.pdf" target="_blank">New Employee Fire Safety Training</a></h3>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; New BYU-Idaho employees are to complete the Fire Safety  Training provided by the Safety&nbsp;Office.&nbsp; The training consist of a  powerpoint presentation followed by a short quiz.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www2.byui.edu/safety/Training%20Files/Firesafetypresentation1.pdf">Click here to take the training</a>.</strong>&nbsp; At the end of the presentation there is a link for the quiz.</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If you have problems with either the presentation or the quiz, please let me know as soon as&nbsp;possible: <a href="mailto:safety@byui.edu" target="_self">safety@byui.edu</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4>SCHEDULED TRAINING</h4>
<blockquote>
<p align="left" style="margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 150%;"><strong>CPR/AED</strong> - 3<sup>rd</sup> Friday morning (8:30 - noon) of each month</p>
<p align="left" style="margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 150%;"><strong>First Aid</strong> - 3<sup>rd</sup> Friday afternoon (1:00 - 4:00) of each month</p>
<p align="left" style="margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 150%;"><strong>Utility Vehicle</strong> Training (Gator &amp; Cart) - 3<sup>rd</sup> Monday (3:00 - 4:00 PM)</p>
<p align="left" style="margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 150%;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 3<sup>rd</sup> Tuesday (9:00 - 10:00 AM)</p>
</blockquote>
<p align="left"><a href="http://www.byui.edu/onlinelearning/" target="_parent"><strong>ON-LINE TRAINING</strong></a></p>
<blockquote>
<p align="left">None available at this time..</p>
</blockquote>
<p align="left"><strong><a href="http://www2.byui.edu/Safety/Videos.htm" target="_parent">TRAINING MATERIALS - VIDEOS</a></strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p align="left">We have training videos available for department use.&nbsp; They are listed on the safety video web site, located <a href="http://www2.byui.edu/Safety/Videos.htm" target="_parent"><strong>here.</strong></a></p>
</blockquote>
<h4 style="margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><a href="http://www2.byui.edu/safety/osha_training.htm" target="_parent">OSHA Training Requirements</a></h4>
<blockquote dir="ltr" style="margin-right: 0px;">
<p align="left" style="margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px;">&nbsp;OSHA has  specified training that must be performed based on certain tasks.&nbsp; This  link lists the required training and the regulations.</p>
</blockquote>
<p align="left" dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px;">&nbsp;<a href="http://www2.byui.edu/Safety/Safety%20Tips/Campus_Training_Matrix.pdf" target="_parent"><strong>TRAINING MATRIX</strong></a></p>
<p align="left" style="margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px;">Not every  job on campus requires the same training in order to perform that job  safely.&nbsp; In order to aid each department in understanding what is  required of a certain position, the training matrix has been developed.&nbsp;  It can be viewed <a href="http://www2.byui.edu/Safety/Safety%20Tips/Campus_Training_Matrix.pdf" target="_parent"><strong>here</strong></a>.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded=""><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="x35774" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required